{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"assign"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","text":"BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"rotatesToMatchCamera"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the value of this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":" and the map is rotated, the annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view rotates. This is also the behavior of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" objects. When the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"value of this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":" the annotation has its rotation angle fixed."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The default value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"text":". Set this property to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"text":" if the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view’s rotation is important.","type":"text"}]}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"title":"rotatesToMatchCamera","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(py)rotatesToMatchCamera","fragments":[{"text":"rotatesToMatchCamera","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"property","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L193"},"roleHeading":"Instance Property","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"rotatesToMatchCamera","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/rotatesToMatchCamera"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/rotatestomatchcamera"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"A Boolean value that determines whether the annotation view rotates together","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with the map.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotationView"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationImage":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for presenting point-based"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotations visually on a map view. Annotation image objects wrap "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIImage"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects and may be recycled later and put into a reuse queue that is maintained"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"by the map view."}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationimage","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationImage","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotationImage","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","role":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"MLNAnnotation"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/rotatesToMatchCamera":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/rotatestomatchcamera","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/rotatesToMatchCamera","role":"symbol","title":"rotatesToMatchCamera","fragments":[{"text":"rotatesToMatchCamera","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value that determines whether the annotation view rotates together"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with the map."}]}}}